Name: Queen of Honor
About the game: Queen of Honor - is a classical 2D platformer with surviving elements where you have to do different levels as a brave queen Hola. The main aim is collecting definite items, letters, find them and you are on the next level. After collecting all letters, you will be opened the door to the queen's house. Come through it and you are on the next level. Be careful as you will meet various traps touching them your hero will die. You have three lives for doing the level, that's why the game is really hardcore. Good luck!
